Here is the API I'm going for (using #378) :

``` js
instantsearch.widgets.clearAllRefinedValues({
  container: '#clear-all-link',
  cssClasses: {root, header, item, link, footer},
  templates: {
    header: '',
    item: '<a class="{{ cssClasses.link }}" href="{{url}}">Clear all</a>', // Called with {cssClasses, url}
    footer: ''
  },
  hideContainerWhenNoRefinements: true
})
```

I didn't include the `label` parameter from the main API proposal because we don't have such a thing in the stats widget which is also using constant text.
